	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64618721"><p>There is always the problem where stupid people use any tool poorly.   You could theoretically use a hammer to knock down a tree, but there are better tools available if that is what you want to do.   Going online to find information isn't an intelligent use of AI, but if you have current tools for you business, using AI to make use of those tools and simplify your workflow won't come up with factually incorrect nonsense, because you aren't using AI to be creative.</p></div>
	</div>

